Title: Planting a Willow
---
I planted a willow tree in the garden
to bind my loverâ€™s horse.
But he snapped a branch and made a whip
to speed his horse away.

I would make a whip from every branch,
and urge my horse behind him..
But the countless limbs of the willow
tie down my bittemess.
